Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Third Man
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xrnd
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 12 Oct 1986
Remembering three great men who resigned high office on points of principle. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.